Template: ebox-control-center/publicip
Type: string
Description: Public IP address
 Please enter the public IP address from the host

Template: ebox-control-center/soapport
Type: string
Default: 4430
Description: SOAP Server Port
 Please enter the port where the Apache SOAP Web server will be listening to

Template: ebox-control-center/vpnaddress
Type: string
Default: 10.0.0.0/24
Description: The Virtual Private Network to use
 Please enter the Virtual Private Network to communicate the control center with eBoxes in CIDR format

Template: ebox-control-center/vpnport
Type: string
Default: 11111
Description: The port where OpenVPN server will be listening to
 Please enter the port where OpenVPN server will be listening to

Template: ebox-control-center/vpnprotocol
Type: select
Choices: tcp, udp
Default: udp
Description: The protocol which OpenVPN server will use
 Please enter the protocol which OpenVPN server will use

Template: ebox-control-center/orgname
Type: string
Default: Network
Description: Organization name for the CA
 Please enter the organization name the CA for the control center

Template: ebox-control-center/days
Type: string
Default: 3650
Description: Number of days the CA will be valid
 Please enter the number of days till the CA for the control center will be valid